<div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_floating_style a2a_vertical_style hidden-xs" style="top:200px;">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-vertical" style="margin-top:-50px" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#zpetna-vazba">
      <p id="vazba-text">Zpětná vazba</p>
    </button>
</div>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="zpetna-vazba" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h4 class="modal-title"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment" aria-hidden="true"></span> Pošli nám odezvu na nový ksi web</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Máš nějaký tip nebo nápad, co a jak zlepšit? Vyskočila na tebe nějaká chyba?</p>

        <p><b>Dej nám vědět, ať s tím můžeme něco dělat.</b></p>

        <textarea class="form-control" rows="3" style="resize:none;"></textarea>
        <br>
        <p><b>Tvá mailová adresa - volitelně</b></p>

        <p>Abychom se když tak mohli doptat na detaily.</p>

        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="zpetna-vazba-email" placeholder="Email">
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 200px">Odeslat odezvu</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="//static.addtoany.com/menu/page.js"></script>

<div class="modal fade" id="login-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
     <div class="loginmodal-container">
    <p data-toggle="modal" data-target="#login-modal" style="margin-left:20px; text-align: right;">
          <a href="javascript:void(0)">zavřít</a>
    </p>
     <div align="center">
             <img src="img/karlik_color.png" style="max-width:200px; vertical-align: middle;"/>
     </div>
    <br>
    {{#if login_error_message}}
      {{login_error_message}}
    {{/if}}
      <form>
      {{input value=identification placeholder="e-mail"}}
        {{input type="password" value=password placeholder="heslo"}}
        <input type="submit" name="login"  class="btn btn-primary" value="Přihlas se" {{action 'login'}}>
      </form>

      <div class="login-help">
      <p data-toggle="modal" data-target="#login-modal" style="margin-left:20px; text-align: right;">{{#link-to "registration"}}Registrovat se{{/link-to}} - {{#link-to "forgot-password"}}Zapomenuté heslo{{/link-to}}</p> <!-- TODO toogle button -->
      </div>
     </div>
  </div>
</div>

